==History and status by continent and country==

=== North America ===

==== Canada ====
{{Main|Indigenous peoples in Canada}}
[[File:Raven-and-the-first-men.jpg|thumb|left|Bill Reid's sculpture '''The Raven and The First Men'''. The Raven represents the [[Trickster]] figure common to many mythologies.]]
